qas.question: Where does the majority of the Burmese country fall on the globe ?

answers.text: Much of the country lies between the Tropic of Cancer and the Equator

qas.question: How much rain is received in the region where Burma is located ?
What is the expected rainfall in the zone considered to be dry in Burma ?
What is the average temperature of the coldest  part of Burma and where is it located ?

answers.text: The Northern regions of Myanmar are the coolest, with average temperatures of 21 °C (70 °F).

qas.question: How warm does it get at the height of summer along the in the delta and coastal regions of Burma?

answers.text: Coastal and delta regions have an average maximum temperature of 32 °C (89.6 °F).
